title: Kenny Burrell - Up The Street, 'Round The Corner,
description:
Kenny Burrell - Up The Street, 'Round The Corner, Down The Block 
Released: 1974 
Label: Fantasy  
Format: Vinyl, LP
Bitrate: 320 kbps

Great mid 70s session from Kenny Burrell with that typical Fantasy fusion sound featuring the old club fave "Up The Street etc" by Onaje Alan Gumbs, a couple of Burrell originals, "Afro Blue" and a closing 9 minute workout of Richard Evans' "Soulero".

Personnel:
Kenny Burrell-Guitar
Jerome Richardson-Flute,Saxes
Richard Wyands-Electric Piano
Andy Simpkins-Bass
Lenny McBrowne-Drums
Mayuto Correa-Percussion

Kenny Burrell - Up The Street, 'Round The Corner, Down The Block Tracks:
01  A1   Up The Street, 'Round The Corner, Down The Block 7:18 
02  A2   Afro Blue 5:40
03  A3   Sausalito Nights 7:15
04  B1   Juice 5:40 
05  B2   A Little Walking Music 3:18
06  B3   Soulero 9:13
